body: Apologies, very strange issue. If I specified `model_dir` as `/home/<user_name>/<directory>/tensorflow`, the tfevents file wasn't generated. But if I changed the `model_dir` to `/home/<user_name>/<directory>/tensorflow123` or to `/tmp/tensorflow`, the tfevents file was present. Closing this issue.
